1
00:00:08,920 --> 00:00:10,380
Miss, please bear with it.

2
00:00:11,680 --> 00:00:13,880
Doctor, how is my wife?

3
00:00:14,480 --> 00:00:15,440
Commander, rest assured.

4
00:00:15,440 --> 00:00:17,480
Luckily, the bullet hit her left shoulder

5
00:00:17,480 --> 00:00:18,880
and missed vital organs.

6
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:20,680
Once we remove the bullet,

7
00:00:20,680 --> 00:00:22,360
she will recover in time.

8
00:00:22,360 --> 00:00:23,040
Good.

9
00:00:33,440 --> 00:00:34,920
My sister has always been pampered.

10
00:00:34,920 --> 00:00:37,050
How can she stand such a severe injury?

11
00:00:38,520 --> 00:00:40,720
Is your sister afraid of pain?

12
00:00:40,720 --> 00:00:41,960
Since childhood, if she even scraped her skin,

13
00:00:41,960 --> 00:00:43,160
she would cry for half a day.

14
00:00:43,160 --> 00:00:44,920
Let alone a gunshot wound.

15
00:00:49,160 --> 00:00:51,360
You are quite tough, not making a sound.

16
00:00:51,560 --> 00:00:53,360
I've suffered worse injuries.

17
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:04,519
Huainan.

18
00:01:04,519 --> 00:01:05,440
I'm here.

19
00:01:11,720 --> 00:01:12,520
Huainan.

20
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:15,320
It's okay. It's okay.

21
00:01:15,320 --> 00:01:16,440
Commander, I will take my leave.

22
00:01:16,440 --> 00:01:17,200
You may go.

23
00:01:20,240 --> 00:01:21,039
Doctor.

24
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:22,600
How is it going in there?

25
00:01:22,600 --> 00:01:23,760
How is my sister?

26
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:26,039
The patient is temporarily out of danger,

27
00:01:26,039 --> 00:01:28,080
but her body is still very weak.

28
00:01:28,520 --> 00:01:30,050
Can we go inside and see her?

29
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:31,200
Yes, you may.

30
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:32,320
Thank you.

31
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:52,520
Shengsheng.

32
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:55,800
How are you? Does the wound still hurt?

33
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:57,520
The bullet is out.

34
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:59,120
I'm fine, Brother.

35
00:01:59,320 --> 00:02:01,520
You're so pale, yet you say you're fine.

36
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:04,800
You've really suffered.

37
00:02:11,200 --> 00:02:12,000
I apologize.

38
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,760
We failed to protect your sister.

39
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:16,480
It is the Song family's negligence.

40
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:17,320
Rest assured.

41
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:19,079
I will do my best to heal her.

42
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:21,960
Brother, I'm really fine.

43
00:02:22,079 --> 00:02:23,800
Father must have been worried sick.

44
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,160
Go and comfort him.

45
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:27,960
Huainan is taking care of me. Don't worry.

46
00:02:30,079 --> 00:02:31,840
Brother, let me get

47
00:02:34,440 --> 00:02:36,800
a military doctor for Sister-in-law.

48
00:02:37,160 --> 00:02:38,680
For these knife and gunshot wounds,

49
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:40,880
military medicine is much better than the hospital's.

50
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:42,520
Okay, go ahead.

51
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,200
Now that you've seen her,

52
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,680
you should all leave.

53
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:47,140
Shengsheng needs to rest.

54
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:59,360
Shengsheng, why are you so silly?

55
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:02,210
Why did a frail woman like you take a bullet for me?

56
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:04,840
I only had one thought in my mind then.

57
00:03:05,920 --> 00:03:08,050
I couldn't let anyone hurt my husband.

58
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:12,240
I'm sorry. I doubted you before.

59
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:14,640
I didn't realize

60
00:03:14,640 --> 00:03:16,200
that I meant so much to you.

61
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,640
If you doubt me again,

62
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,329
I'll have to punish you.

63
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:23,880
Get some rest.

64
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:26,480
I'll check if the medicine is ready.

65
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:28,280
Come back soon.

66
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:28,920
Okay.

67
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:37,720
Two days from now, at the Song house,

68
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,800
send a hitman to shoot Song Huainan.

69
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,720
Dead or alive.

70
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,530
Here is the deposit.

71
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,959
Shengsheng, are you okay?

72
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:28,920
Shengsheng.

73
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,560
What's wrong? It's Huainan.

74
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:37,880
Huainan.

75
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:42,760
I... I just had a nightmare.

76
00:04:45,080 --> 00:04:47,140
It must be the trauma from yesterday.

77
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:50,080
It's okay. Everything will be fine.

78
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:18,920
Yao Shengsheng, why are you

79
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,440
resisting me so much?

80
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:22,720
Yesterday, you risked your life to save me.

81
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:24,200
But look at you now.

82
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:29,730
Yao Shengsheng,

83
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:32,290
I really can't figure you out anymore.

84
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:35,480
I...

85
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:38,640
Guards!

86
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,280
Young Master.

87
00:05:41,840 --> 00:05:43,280
Guard the Madam's door.

88
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,690
Without my permission,

89
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:46,200
no one is allowed to see her.

90
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:46,880
Yes, sir.

91
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:03,760
Brother,

92
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:07,000
why did you lock Yao Shengsheng up?

93
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,280
I locked your sister-in-law up

94
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:09,600
so she can reflect on herself.

95
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,440
It's also a chance for her to heal.

96
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:12,240
What's wrong?

97
00:06:12,320 --> 00:06:13,320
Heal?

98
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,080
If during this time,

99
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:17,800
something happens to her, what will you do?

100
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:20,400
Don't forget.

101
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:23,080
Yao Shengsheng took a bullet for you.

102
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:25,120
You didn't take good care of her,

103
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,520
and even restricted her freedom.

104
00:06:26,520 --> 00:06:28,320
What does that have to do with you?

105
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:30,640
Song Qingzhou, I've told you many times.

106
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:32,770
She is your sister-in-law and my wife.

107
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,320
It is not your place to interfere.

108
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:35,920
You'd better stay away from her.

109
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:36,400
How dare you...

110
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:37,120
Shut up.

111
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,920
One more word and I'll lock you up too.

112
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:39,680
Lock me up, then.

113
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,800
Do you think I won't?

114
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,000
Of course you will.

115
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,720
You wouldn't just lock me up.

116
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:46,280
You'd even dare to kill me.

117
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:47,240
Bullshit.

118
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,360
My dear brother.

119
00:07:00,960 --> 00:07:02,760
The day I was chasing deserters,

120
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:05,400
the one who shot me in the back

121
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:07,530
was your man, wasn't it?

122
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:10,130
What did you say?

123
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,880
Adjutant Li has followed you for years,

124
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:13,200
risked his life for you,

125
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:15,000
and handles your dirty work.

126
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:17,720
Who else could make him shoot me

127
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:19,960
but you?

128
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:28,120
Brother, do you want me dead that badly?

129
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:30,760
What the hell are you saying?

130
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:33,240
If anyone else touched a hair on your head,

131
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,840
I'd have their head.

132
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:37,040
Yet you think I want to kill you?

133
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:39,840
That's right. It was Adjutant Li who hurt you that day.

134
00:07:39,840 --> 00:07:41,100
But it was an accident.

135
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:43,280
I sent him to investigate something else.

136
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:45,080
Besides, I've already shot him.

137
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:47,760
Investigate something else?

138
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:48,760
What was it?

139
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:50,020
You don't need to know.

140
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,680
Song Qingzhou, let me tell you.

141
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:53,520
Anyone else can blame me,

142
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:54,480
but not you.

143
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,400
Everything I've done

144
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:57,260
is for the sake of our Song family.

145
00:07:57,840 --> 00:07:59,840
If I hear such rebellious words again,

146
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:01,040
get out.

147
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:11,160
Marshal,

148
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,880
the adjutant reported that Ambassador Johnson

149
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:14,680
has matters to discuss with you.

150
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:18,420
I'll deal with you when I get back.

151
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:35,720
Second Young Master.

152
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:36,960
Move aside.

153
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:37,799
But...

154
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:39,200
the Eldest Young Master ordered that no one

155
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:41,039
disturb the Eldest Young Mistress's rest.

156
00:08:41,039 --> 00:08:42,770
Since you call me Young Master,

157
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:44,660
you should know who the master is.

158
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:46,160
Get lost.

159
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:47,480
Yes.

160
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,330
Yao Shengsheng.

161
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,040
So this is your plan?

162
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:59,760
Hiring someone to assassinate my brother, and then taking a bullet for him?

163
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:01,290
Aren't you afraid of dying?

164
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,560
You figured it out.

165
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,800
What if something went wrong

166
00:09:05,560 --> 00:09:07,160
and you lost your life there?

167
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:15,600
You schemed to marry into the Song family.

168
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:16,920
How far will you go

169
00:09:16,920 --> 00:09:17,960
before you stop?

170
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:20,200
Until the Song family

171
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,480
pays back everything

172
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:26,160
they owe me.

173
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:32,000
If you keep taking risks like this,

174
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:34,600
do you really think you'll live to see that day?

175
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,520
Zhu Luoli.
